text: Nataliya Naranovich (born 1 August 1981) is a Belarusian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Minsk
